个省份推行。 在中国直接取用地表水或者地下水的单位和个人，为水资源税纳税人，应当按规定缴纳水资源税。一般情况水资源税按照取水量乘以适用税额来定，而具体适用税额由各省确定，但国家给了各省一个最低平均税额，比如四川、上海等13个省份地表水最低税额不得低于0.1元/立方米，而北京这一标准为1.6元/立方米。 为何要在全国推广水资源费改税？这与中国水资源匮乏，而水资源费不能很好发挥促进水资源节约作用，而水资源税可以扭转这一情况。 目前中国人均水资源量远低于世界平均水平，而且分布不均，16个省份面临着水资源危机，多达300个城市存在不同程度地缺水。12月起31个省份将全部用水资源税替代此前收费，水价会涨吗？专家解读_腾讯新闻"},"attached_info":"CkEIxLLUyp6TnfdbEAMaCTExMTE4NTgzMSDBpr24BjAAOJ0BQANyCjEwNDUxNTg4NDN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"167 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-0db5c2e59eb5586dcbdb41710aa48243_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1729675188.585188","card_id":"Q_1641394376","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":1641394376,"title":"高振宁为什么要开团《英雄联盟》解说王多多？王多多解说真的有问题吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1641394376","type":"question","created":1729547708,"answer_count":111,"follower_count":141,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[18427,154337,389649,404074,3066798],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkEIxLLUyp6TnfdbEAMaCTExMTMwNDk4MyC8m9u4BjAAOI0BQARyCjE2NDEzOTQzNzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"163 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-a8bf677cb7088911ebf8044037cb078f_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1729675188.585369","card_id":"Q_1733639100","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":1733639100,"title":"如何看待水果猎人杨晓洋质疑山取团队「哀牢山摆拍」?","url":"https